蓬莱 · Penglai
================

Penglai (蓬莱) is a downstream *distribution* of GenericAgent — the GA kernel is
kept at zero diff and all Penglai capabilities are mounted as additive files /
runtime plugins (like Ubuntu to the Linux kernel). This NOTICE records the
copyright and brand boundaries that the single root LICENSE (upstream MIT) does
not, by itself, make obvious to license scanners or downstream users.


